==English==

===Verb===
'''to calcine'''

#{{transitive}} to [[heat]] something without [[melting]] in order to drive off [[water]] etc, and to [[decompose]] [[carbonate]]s into [[oxide]]s or to [[oxidize]] or [[reduce]] it; especially to heat [[limestone]] to form [[quicklime]]
#{{intransitive}} to undergo such heating

